On June 19th, National Watch Day recognizes an industry that has been around for more than 500 years and is steadily evolving. Choosing a watch is very personal as the choices are vast and numerous. Even with the advent of smartphones and smartwatches, the classic wristwatch signals individual taste, culture, and a rich history that cannot be disputed.

* * * * *
El 19 de junio, el National Watch Day reconoce una industria que ha existido durante más de 500 años y está en constante evolución. Elegir un reloj es muy personal ya que las opciones son amplias y numerosas. Incluso con la llegada de los teléfonos inteligentes y los relojes inteligentes, el reloj de pulsera clásico muestra el gusto individual, la cultura y una rica historia que no se puede disputar.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl
[sources: National Day Calendar, Omega Watch Co.]

post_text:
On June 17th get whirled up in pastry dough, apples and spices and celebrate National Apple Strudel Day. In German, the word strudel means whirlpool or eddy. This tasty dessert is perfectly described by its German language as the sweet mixture of fruit, sugar, spices, and layers of thin dough rolled together and baked. The result is a bubbling, flaky treat.

* * * * *
El 17 de junio, mézclate con masa de hojaldre, manzanas y especias y celebra el Día Nacional del Strudel de Manzana. En alemán, la palabra strudel significa remolino o remolino. Este sabroso postre está perfectamente descrito por su idioma alemán como la dulce mezcla de fruta, azúcar, especias y capas de masa fina enrollada y horneada. El resultado es una delicia burbujeante y escamosa.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl
[sources: National Day Calendar]

post_text:
National Fudge Day comes around each year on June 16th, allowing you to indulge in your favorite flavor of this delicious confectionery. Some of the most familiar fudge flavors are chocolate, chocolate nut, peanut butter, maple, and maple nut.

* * * * *
El Día Nacional del Dulce de Azúcar se celebra cada año el 16 de junio, lo que le permite disfrutar de su sabor favorito de esta deliciosa confitería. Algunos de los sabores de chocolate más familiares son el chocolate, la nuez de chocolate, la mantequilla de maní, el arce y la nuez de arce.
・・・

A medida que nos acercamos al primer día de verano, el 11 de junio marca el calendario para celebrar el Día Nacional del Maíz en la Mazorca cada año. post_text:
National Iced Tea Day on June 10th each year celebrates one of summer’s favorite drinks. Whether you prefer sweetened or unsweetened, with or without lemon, many love and enjoy iced tea by the glass full all summer long.

Creating your custom iced tea is as easy as adding a hint of flavor. Whether you add a squeeze of lemon or the juice of raspberries, lime, passion fruit, strawberry, or cherry, make your iced tea your way.

* * * * *
El Día Nacional del Té Helado, el 10 de junio de cada año, celebra una de las bebidas favoritas del verano. Ya sea que prefiera endulzado o sin endulzar, con o sin limón, a muchos les encanta y disfrutan de un té helado en un vaso lleno durante todo el verano.

Crear su té helado personalizado es tan fácil como agregar un toque de sabor. Ya sea que agregue un poco de limón o el jugo de frambuesas, lima, maracuyá, fresa o cereza, haga su té helado a su manera.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl
[sources: National Day Calendar]

World Oceans Day takes place every 8 June. It is an annual observation to honor, help protect, and conserve the world’s oceans. The ocean provides us with many resources and services including oxygen, climate regulation, food sources, medicine, and more.

* * * * *
El Día Mundial de los Océanos se celebra cada 8 de junio. Es una observación anual para honrar, ayudar a proteger y conservar los océanos del mundo. El océano nos proporciona muchos recursos y servicios que incluyen oxígeno, regulación climática, fuentes de alimentos, medicamentos y más.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl

post_text:
On June 8th, honor your closest and dearest friend on Best Friends Day.

The relationship between best friends is often fierce and can withstand distance, storms and silence. Whether we’ve known them all our lives or they are more recently acquired, best friends make tough times bearable, fun times memorable, and memorable times priceless.

* * * * *
El 8 de junio, honra a tu amigo más querido en el Día de los Mejores Amigos.

La relación entre los mejores amigos es a menudo feroz y puede soportar la distancia, las tormentas y el silencio. Ya sea que los hayamos conocido toda nuestra vida o que los hayamos adquirido más recientemente, los mejores amigos hacen que los tiempos difíciles sean soportables, los momentos divertidos y los momentos memorables no tengan precio.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl

June 5, every year is celebrated as World Environment Day or WED. The day is set aside to encourage awareness and action to protect the natural environment. It draws attention to environmental issues such as marine pollution, air pollution, deforestation, and wildlife crime such as poaching.

* * * * *
El 5 de junio, cada año se celebra como el Día Mundial del Medio Ambiente o WED. El día está reservado para fomentar la conciencia y la acción para proteger el medio ambiente natural. Llama la atención sobre cuestiones ambientales como la contaminación marina, la contaminación del aire, la deforestación y los delitos contra la vida silvestre, como la caza furtiva.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl

post_text:
June 2nd is a day made for chocolate, marshmallows, and nuts. It’s National Rocky Road Day! In the United States, the most popular way to eat Rocky Road is in ice cream.

Although there are many variations, traditionally, Rocky Road ice cream was made of chocolate ice cream, nuts, and marshmallows. Today, there are variations with vanilla ice cream, chocolate chips, and almonds.

* * * * *
El 2 de junio es un día hecho para chocolate, malvaviscos y nueces. ¡Es el Día Nacional de Rocky Road! En los Estados Unidos, la forma más popular de comer Rocky Road es con helado.

Aunque hay muchas variaciones, tradicionalmente, el helado Rocky Road estaba hecho de helado de chocolate, nueces y malvaviscos. Hoy en día, hay variaciones con helado de vainilla, chispas de chocolate y almendras.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl
[sources: National Day Calendar]

Whether you are an artist, writer, musician, filmmaker, blogger, photographer, graphic artist, or any of 100 other creative personalities, the world is going to celebrate you and your creative pursuit. ¡Da rienda suelta a tu imaginación el 30 de mayo para el Día Nacional de la Creatividad!

Si usted es artista, escritor, músico, cineasta, blogger, fotógrafo, artista gráfico o cualquiera de las otras 100 personalidades creativas, el mundo lo celebrará a usted y a su búsqueda creativa. ¡Y te lo mereces absolutamente! ¡Aparte de la naturaleza, todo a la vista se originó con un pensamiento creativo de alguien como tú!

post_text:
National Hamburger Day on May 28th wraps up National Burger Month and also ushers in summer grilling season.

Hamburger. Seasoned ground beef, grilled and placed between two slices of bread or a bun. Topped with sauteed onions, peppers, pickles, sliced onions, or cheese. Add condiments such as ketchup, mustard, or mayo. Anyone of these combinations would create a modern American version a hamburger.

* * * * *
El Día Nacional de la Hamburguesa el 28 de mayo concluye el Mes Nacional de la Hamburguesa y también marca el comienzo de la temporada de parrilladas de verano.

Hamburguesa. Carne molida sazonada, a la parrilla y colocada entre dos rebanadas de pan o un bollo. Cubierto con cebollas salteadas, pimientos, pepinillos, cebollas en rodajas o queso. Agregue condimentos como salsa de tomate, mostaza o mayonesa. Cualquiera de estas combinaciones crearía una versión americana moderna de una hamburguesa.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl

Each year on May 22nd, National Maritime Day recognizes the launch of the maritime industry in the United States. The celebration also honors America’s Merchant Marines for their contributions and sacrifices for our country. Special acknowledgment is given to ships and seafarers that have held a prominent place in our nation’s history.

* * * * *
Cada año, el 22 de mayo, el Día Marítimo Nacional reconoce el lanzamiento de la industria marítima en los Estados Unidos. La celebración también rinde homenaje a los marines mercantes de Estados Unidos por sus contribuciones y sacrificios por nuestro país. Se otorga un reconocimiento especial a los barcos y la gente de mar que han ocupado un lugar destacado en la historia de nuestra nación.

post_text:
Pandemic EBT

Due to Coronavirus (COVID-19), children who are eligible for free or reduced-price meals at school will get extra food benefits. These food benefits are called Pandemic EBT or P-EBT benefits. P-EBT benefits help families in California buy food when schools are closed because of the coronavirus emergency.

Families will get up to $365 per eligible child on their P-EBT card to use on food and groceries.

Families with children who get CalFresh, Medi-Cal or Foster Care benefits do not need to apply. Most will get their P-EBT card in the mail during the month of May. P-EBT cards will begin arriving around May 12, 2020.

Families with children who are eligible for free or reduced-price meals and who do not get their P-EBT card in the mail by about May 22, 2020 must apply online before June 30, 2020. The online application will be available beginning May 22, 2020 at ca.p-ebt.org.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl

World Bee Day is celebrated on May 20 each year. The purpose of the international day is to acknowledge the role of bees and other pollinators for the ecosystem.

Every year on this day, the global public will focus on the importance of preserving honey bees and all other pollinators. People will be reminded of the significance of bees in providing for the needs of humanity.

* * * * *
El Día Mundial de la Abeja se celebra el 20 de mayo de cada año. El propósito del día internacional es reconocer el papel de las abejas y otros polinizadores para el ecosistema.

Todos los años en este día, el público mundial se centrará en la importancia de preservar las abejas melíferas y todos los demás polinizadores. Se recordará a la gente la importancia de las abejas para satisfacer las necesidades de la humanidad.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl

Everyone reacts differently to stressful situations like COVID-19. You may feel anxiousness, anger, sadness, or overwhelmed. Find ways to reduce your stress to help yourself and the people you care about.

• Learn the common signs of stress.
• Make time to unwind and do activities you enjoy.
• Talk with family and friends by phone, text, or email.
• If you or a loved one is feeling overwhelmed, get support 24/7 by calling 1-800-985-5990 or text TalkWithUs to 66746.

Learn more about stress and coping during the COVID-19 outbreak: https://bit.ly/39UVoEj.

International Day of Families is a UN observance every 15 May. The day has been observed since 1995, on the heals of the International Year of Families in 1994. It is a time to remember the crucial role the family plays in our world’s cultures and societies.

* * * * *
El Día Internacional de las Familias se celebra cada 15 de mayo. El día se ha observado desde 1995, en las curaciones del Año Internacional de las Familias en 1994. Es un momento para recordar el papel crucial que juega la familia en las culturas y sociedades de nuestro mundo.
・・・

shared_text:
CDC
May 14 at 10:21 AM ·

Are you caring for someone who has or might have COVID-19? Lower the chance of others getting sick:
✔️ The person who is sick should stay in a separate area of the home, if possible.
✔️ Only clean the area around the person who is sick when needed, such as when the area is soiled. This will help limit your contact with the sick person.
✔️ In other areas of the home, clean and disinfect high-touch surfaces and items like tables, doorknobs, and cabinet handles each day.
✔️ Clean surfaces with soap and water first, then disinfect.
✔️ Put on gloves and use a household disinfectant. Follow product instructions for contact time, rinsing, and putting chemicals away where children cannot reach them.

Get more tips: https://bit.ly/2WQCYyZ

Protect yourself from COVID-19 when going shopping:
✔️ If possible, order online or use curbside pickup.
✔️ If you have to go in person, avoid
crowds by going early in the morning or later in the evening.
✔️ Wear a face covering, and do not move it or touch your face.
✔️ Stay at least 6 feet away from others.
✔️ If possible, clean your cart with disinfectant wipes.
✔️ Use hand sanitizer with at least 60% alcohol after paying.
✔️ Wash your hands with soap and water after leaving the store and after you put away your items.

Get more tips: https://bit.ly/34ucuqJ

National Fitness Day on the first Saturday in May offers an opportunity to be inspired and try new ways of becoming fit and healthy.

The day is dedicated to everyone – not just health enthusiasts. Step out and try a class that looks interesting. Zumba? Yoga? Yes, try it for a day. Perhaps you only want to get out and stretch. Do it!

* * * * *
El Día Nacional de Fitness el primer sábado de mayo ofrece la oportunidad de inspirarse y probar nuevas formas de estar en forma y saludable.

El día está dedicado a todos, no solo a los entusiastas de la salud. Sal y prueba una clase que parezca interesante. Zumba? ¿Yoga? Sí, pruébalo por un día. Quizás solo quieras salir y estirarte. ¡Hazlo!
・・・

post_text:
National Space Day, dedicates the first Friday in May, to the extraordinary achievements, benefits, and opportunities in the exploration and use of space. The goal of the observance is to promote math, science, technology, and engineering education in young people, The hope is to inspire them to pursue a career in science, especially a career in space-related jobs.

* * * * *
El Día Nacional del Espacio, dedica el primer viernes de mayo, a los logros, beneficios y oportunidades extraordinarios en la exploración y uso del espacio. El objetivo de la celebración es promover la educación en matemáticas, ciencias, tecnología e ingeniería en los jóvenes. La esperanza es inspirarlos a seguir una carrera en ciencias, especialmente una carrera en trabajos relacionados con el espacio.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl

post_text:
They say that love is the universal force that binds us all. With such a powerful impact, it’s only right to dedicate an entire day to all the positivity that love brings. Global Love Day is just that occasion.

This annual celebration is carried out on May 1st, to remind humanity that anything can be achieved when we attune our minds to the frequency of unconditional love.

* * * * *
Dicen que el amor es la fuerza universal que nos une a todos. Con un impacto tan poderoso, es correcto dedicar un día entero a toda la positividad que trae el amor. El Día Mundial del Amor es solo esa ocasión.

Esta celebración anual se lleva a cabo el 1 de mayo, para recordarle a la humanidad que cualquier cosa se puede lograr cuando sintonizamos nuestras mentes con la frecuencia del amor incondicional.
・・・
#altapublicschools #ibschool #internationalbaccalaureate #education #school #collegebound #steameducation #careerfocus #family #lead #learn #rigor #lrfl

Each 30 April has been celebrated as International Jazz Day since 2012. This UN observance is meant to celebrate the cultural contributions of jazz music as well as to try to use the wide popularity of jazz to unite people all around the world and promote world peace.

* * * * *
Cada 30 de abril se celebra como el Día Internacional del Jazz desde 2012. Esta celebración de la ONU está destinada a celebrar las contribuciones culturales de la música de jazz, así como a tratar de utilizar la amplia popularidad del jazz para unir a las personas de todo el mundo y promover la paz mundial.
・・・

shared_text:
Dr. Jane Goodall
April 24 at 3:26 PM ·

It's the best part of the week! Join Dr. Jane for a virtual reading of 'Me...Jane'! Patrick McDonnell (author of MUTTS) tells the story of the young Jane Goodall and her special childhood toy chimpanzee named Jubilee. As the young Jane observes the natural world around her with wonder, she dreams of "a life living with and helping all animals," until one day she finds that her dream has come true.

Every week Dr. Jane will share some of her books with you at home, from her home in Bournemouth, England as we all practice #socialdistancing. Learn more at storytime.janegoodall.org.

Have kids learning from home? Check out the Roots & Shoots USA 'Learn at Home' page with FREE weekly at home activity schedules: rootsandshoots.org/learn-at-home

#StorieswithDrJane
